---
---

<section class="section meet-roy" id="meet-roy">
  <div class="container-wide">
    <div class="meet-roy__layout">
      <div class="meet-roy__visual reveal">
        <div class="meet-roy__image-wrap">
          <img
            src="/assets/roy/roy-teaching.jpg"
            alt="Roy Faust teaching at a desk with architectural drawings behind him"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="meet-roy__stats">
          <div>
            <strong>20+</strong>
            <span>Years in the trenches</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>$50M+</strong>
            <span>In residential remodels</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>0</strong>
            <span>Sponsors or upsells</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="meet-roy__content reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">MEET THE WOLF</span>
        <h2>Roy Faust is the guy homeowners call<br />when the job goes sideways.</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          For over 20 years, Roy has run one of the most successful remodeling companies
          in Austin, Texas. He's seen it all — the good contractors, the bad ones, the scams,
          the wins, and every expensive mistake a homeowner can make.
        </p>

        <p>
          After helping countless friends, colleagues, and family members navigate their own
          remodels — often pulling them out of messes that could have been avoided with a
          little insider knowledge — Roy decided it was time to share what he knows with
          more people. Not as a contractor pitching a service. As the guy on your side of
          the table.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Roy's only client now is you.</strong>
        </p>

        <div class="meet-roy__creds">
          <div class="meet-roy__cred">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41M17.66 17.66l1.41 1.41M2 12h2M20 12h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
            <span>Homeowner advocate first, always</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meet-roy__cred">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span>Decades of field experience across every room &amp; trade</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meet-roy__cred">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
            <span>Available live, every Friday, for members</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .meet-roy { background: var(--bg-alt); }
  .meet-roy__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.15fr;
    gap: 4.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .meet-roy__visual { position: relative; }
  .meet-roy__image-wrap {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .meet-roy__image-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .meet-roy__stats {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--gtw-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    width: max-content;
    max-width: 95%;
  }
  .meet-roy__stats > div {
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .meet-roy__stats > div:last-child { border-right: 0; }
  .meet-roy__stats strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--gtw-blue);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .meet-roy__stats span {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .meet-roy__content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--gtw-dark);
  }
  .meet-roy__content .lead {
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .meet-roy__content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .meet-roy__content p strong {
    color: var(--gtw-dark);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .meet-roy__creds {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.8rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .meet-roy__cred {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gtw-dark);
  }
  .meet-roy__cred svg {
    color: var(--gtw-orange);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .meet-roy__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
    .meet-roy__visual {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .meet-roy__stats {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }
    .meet-roy__stats > div {
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-right: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }
    .meet-roy__stats > div:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  }
</style>
